{"tid":2393054,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵一套三年前睇過嘅漫畫","createTime":"2021-02-03T07:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T20:28:48.000Z","uid":46748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"502f81287480260e323a815aad9bb928be13dad0","tid":2393054,"uid":46748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"內容大概係講男主角屋企人細個俾另一個種族既殺哂，暫稱呢個種族做鬼 因為唔係好記得叫咩<br />\n咁男主就發奮報仇 練到好似好勁咁<br />\n有一日佢被委派去保護一個女仔 人類嚟<br />\n點知原來個女仔嗰家人除咗佢之外全部都係鬼嚟<br />\n個女仔係俾鬼湊大<br />\n男主角就心諗：[無理由架 全部鬼都會殺人 係仆街含家鏟嚟 無理由會湊大一個人類女仔架]<br />\n跟住男主就去觀察下班鬼會唔會有咩企圖咁<br />\n故事發展落去都係化解下啲因因怨怨 打打殺殺咁<br />\n唔知有冇ching睇過呢套野"},{"pid":"e1878b63c7415150fea41add61e864474164549b","tid":2393054,"uid":188310,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:00:01.000Z","msg":"一定係鬼滅之刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2764aacacbbf35712a487b3337bbf084fd8ca12","tid":2393054,"uid":46748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1878b63c7415150fea41add61e864474164549b","tid":2393054,"uid":188310,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:00:01.000Z","msg":"一定係鬼滅之刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:00:35.000Z","msg":"唔係啦 女主角無擔住碌竹"},{"pid":"5d40253e7fd9332433c050d667ae0227a998a638","tid":2393054,"uid":391493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1878b63c7415150fea41add61e864474164549b","tid":2393054,"uid":188310,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:00:01.000Z","msg":"一定係鬼滅之刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:01:14.000Z","msg":"唔係魂減の刅咩？"},{"pid":"6214f74425cd1e6aaba3ef9aee34b3de8916987e","tid":2393054,"uid":46748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:02:15.000Z","msg":"最印象深刻係呢套野有好多二五仔<br />\n你以為佢係忠嘅 點知佢真係忠<br />\n以為佢係奸嘅 點知佢真係奸<br />\n成套無間道咁"},{"pid":"21ea8d5665256941dc013d609e62930bb0